      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">View of the <ref target="http://gams.uni-graz.at/o:siba.glossar?mode=K5">kafana</ref> and vantage point on <ref target="http://gams.uni-graz.at/o:siba.glossar?mode=B1">Babića bašča</ref> hill extending to the <ref target="http://gams.uni-graz.at/o:siba.glossar?mode=B14">Bijela tabija</ref> fort and the mountains beyond on a slightly cloudy summer day. The <ref target="http://gams.uni-graz.at/o:siba.glossar?mode=K5">kafana</ref> includes a gazebo with a tiled roof and a garden terrace with a large gate.</ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet" subtype="comment">The picture is taken from the same spot as siba.4886. Analogue photographic process, negative-positive (Agfa Isopan 17 DIN). Original preserved as a negative-diptych, stored as a negative and a digital record.</ab>
